33 equivalent of the amount determined under subdivision (1)
34 sub-subdivision (1)a. of this subsection, adjusted for the age of the
35 member at the time of retirement or, when appropriate, the age at the
36 time of the member's death.
37 (3)c. Multiply the annuity amount determined under subdivision (2)
38 sub-subdivision (1)b. of this subsection by the contribution-based
39 benefit cap factor.
40 (4)d. Determine the amount of the retirement allowance that results from
